subject: Football (College)
Suits and Litigation (Civil)
lead_paragraph: The former assistant Joe Wickline settled a breach-of-contract lawsuit, which lets Texas Coach Charlie Strong and quarterback Tyrone Swoopes avoid having to testify in an Oklahoma courtroom about who called plays for the Longhorns.
